Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.40,0:00:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,《德古拉》剧情回顾\NPreviously on Dracula...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.48,0:00:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我不需要你的开价\NI do not need to see your offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.32,0:00:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我对出售没有兴趣\NMy interests are not for sale.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.92,0:00:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,无论多少价钱\NAt any price.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.52,0:00:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Grayson先生让我去他的公司上班\NMr. Grayson has offered me a position in his firm.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.82,0:00:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我要你告诉我\NI want you to tell me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.99,0:00:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,关于Laurent大人的一切\Neverything you know about Lord Laurent.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.66,0:00:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你想知道的所有事情\NEverything you need to know you can find out
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.03,0:00:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚10点钟  都在斯温伯恩俱乐部\N10:00 p.M. At the Swinburne Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.37,0:00:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你想要什么？\NWhat do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.43,0:00:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我相信你不会对我调用先知有何异议吧\NI presume you have no objection to my deployment of the seers.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.63,0:00:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,伦敦有个吸血鬼\NThere is a vampire in London.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.17,0:00:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你们要立刻找到他\NYou shall find him forthwith.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.17,0:00:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,他发现了他们\NHe detected them and then employed
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.44,0:00:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,然后采取某种策略\Nsome kind of countermeasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.64,0:00:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我会追击并摧毁他\NI will track him, and I will destroy him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.81,0:00:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么让Harker把那个女人带到您身边？\NWhy engage Harker to bring the woman into your orbit?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.48,0:00:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,无疑您自己就可以轻而易举得到她\NSurely you have the power to simply take her.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.15,0:00:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,把她变的和我一样\NTo turn her into as such as I am,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.82,0:00:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,那会令人憎恶的\Nit would be an abomination.
