Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.10,0:01:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(358,376)\fs24\c&H03FBF9&}====祝大家观影愉快====
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.09,0:02:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,既然命中注定  那就遵循而行\NSo it is written, and so it shall be done.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.70,0:02:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Ilona\NIlona.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.48,0:02:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ilona\NIlona.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.50,0:03:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我在哪？\NWhere am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.90,0:03:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么我没死？\NWhy am I not dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.00,0:03:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是你反抗的价值\NThis is the price of your defiance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.71,0:03:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,用你反抗上帝的力量\NUsing the power of the God you denounced,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.01,0:03:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,恶龙会创造了一个怪物\NOrdo Draco has made a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.44,0:03:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,汝命注定  被判永远在黑暗中徘徊\NThou art condemned, condemned to endless night.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.15,0:03:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,呀！\NYah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.82,0:03:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Vlad Tepes被判为不死之身\NVlad Tepes is condemned to be undead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.06,0:04:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我还不知道您会弹钢琴  先生\NI had no idea you played, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.53,0:04:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,已经有一个多世纪没有摸过琴键了\NIt's been over a century since I last put fingers to keys.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.97,0:04:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我在想Jayne Wetherty女士\NI was thinking about Lady Jayne Wetherby
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.01,0:04:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,还有她明显的不良嗜好\Nand her decidedly unwholesome avocation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.75,0:04:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,您说哪个  先生？\NReally? Which one, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.18,0:04:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,当然是她猎鬼爱好\NHer vampire hunting, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.45,0:04:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,很难去相信\NIt stretches credulity
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.82,0:04:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,她与恶龙会没有任何关系\Nto think she's unaffiliated with the Order.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.52,0:04:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我也同意  先生\NI would tend to agree, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.53,0:04:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,但是她是一介妇人\NBut then she is a female.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.16,0:05:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不论如何\NI suppose I shall have to ascertain it
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.03,0:05:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得我应该查明这事儿\None way or the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.37,0:05:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么？\NWhat's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.10,0:05:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,那个是书面证明\NAh, yes, written confirmation
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.97,0:05:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,来自Laurent大人的律师\Nfrom Lord Laurent's solicitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.94,0:05:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,恭喜您  先生\NCongratulations, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.08,0:05:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,您现在是大英冷剂公司的主要控股人了\NYou are now a majority stockholder of British Imperial Coolant.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.81,0:05:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H03FBF9&\fn华文新魏\fs28\pos(384,334)}—— 德 古 拉 ——\N第一季第三集
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.21,0:06:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Jonathan  哦\NJonathan. Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.57,0:06:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好  你精神不太好啊\NGood morning. You look dreadful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.44,0:06:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,收拾好行李  我们该走了\NPack your trunk and we shall go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.85,0:06:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,去哪？\NGo where?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.18,0:06:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,母亲去巴黎了  把我一个人扔在这\NMother decamped for Paris and left me on my own,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.18,0:06:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你也知道我多讨厌独自生活\Nand you know how much I hate that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.69,0:06:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,所以如果药剂能同时解救我的寂寞\NSo, if the cure for my loneliness and your broken heart
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.89,0:06:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,还有你伤透了的心的话...\Nare the same thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.86,0:06:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么知道的？\NHow did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.93,0:06:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我亲爱的Mina\NDearest Mina,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.16,0:06:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不要为Jonathan Harker落一点泪\Ndo not shed a single tear for Jonathan Harker.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.06,0:06:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,实话说  这毫无意义\NHonestly, there's no point in wasting a single minute more
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.93,0:06:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,别浪费时间去想他变得那混蛋样了\Nthinking about what an awful twit he turned out to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.20,0:06:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,现在你应该和我一起找点乐子\NNot when you could be having fun with me instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.78,0:07:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Murray医生  我手下有两个亲戚\NDr. Murray, I have two young relatives
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.62,0:07:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,聪明伶俐的年轻人\Nunder my charge, sharp, young minds,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.46,0:07:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,但最近他们的精神状态有点儿问题\Nbut lately they've experienced a great, psychic strain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.16,0:07:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道  以您在这里的能力\NI understand, in your capacity as director of this institution,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.70,0:07:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,您一定曾治疗过\Nthat you've had the privilege of serving as an alienist
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.27,0:07:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,很多上流名士吧\Nto certain individuals of high renown.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.14,0:07:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我确实治疗过一些公众人士了\NI have treated a number of public figures.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.54,0:07:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,当然您应理解  我不能泄露…\NYou understand of course that I can't divulge...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.54,0:07:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不不不  您的谨慎是众所周知的\NNo, no, your reputation for discretion precedes you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.38,0:07:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,这也正是我来的原因\NWhich is why I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.61,0:07:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,当然不是为我自己\NNot for myself naturally,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.15,0:07:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,是为了我的亲人\Nbut for close relations
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.42,0:07:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,希望能匿名会诊\Nwho wish to remain anonymous.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.52,0:07:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,那么  需要我怎样帮您？\NPlease, how may I be of service?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.34,0:07:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(372,224)}大英冷剂公司
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.36,0:07:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该确保我们的订单\NYou should be able to meet our order
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.86,0:07:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,没有任何问题  Worth先生\Nwithout a problem, Mr. Worth.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.53,0:07:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你的意思是  要我们把整个运营\NAre you suggesting we dedicate the entirety of our operation
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.57,0:08:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,都只为一个客户而服务吗？\Nto the needs of a single client?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.00,0:08:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不不\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.37,0:08:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我觉得他是这样想的\NBut I think he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.87,0:08:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你们两个  滚出我的办公室  现在！\NGet out of my office now, both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.18,0:08:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,很好  不过我很遗憾的\NVery well. Though I must regretfully
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.08,0:08:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,通知你  你被解雇了\Ninform you that your employment here is terminated,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.92,0:08:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,即刻生效\Neffective immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.86,0:08:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你没有权力解聘我\NYou don't have the authority to dismiss me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.93,0:08:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你除了是个有钱人的狗腿还是什么\NYou're nothing more than a rich man's novelty
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.53,0:08:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我甚至不会让你进我家的门\NI wouldn't even let into my home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.23,0:08:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,稍等一下  你没有权力\NNow hold on a minute. You have no right
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.46,0:08:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这么说…  - 作为大英冷剂公司的\N- to speak... - As a majority shareholder
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.70,0:08:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,主要控股人\Nof British Imperial Lubrication and Coolant Co., limited,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.67,0:08:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Alexander Grayson现在是你的老板\NAlexander Grayson is now your employer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.14,0:08:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我说时  我就拥有他的权力\NWhen I speak, I speak with his authority.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.08,0:08:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我再给你一次机会  照我说的做\NI'll give you a second chance to do as you're told.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.71,0:08:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我说的够清楚了吗？\NHave I made myself clear?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.35,0:09:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.12,0:09:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,先生\NSir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.33,0:09:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,希望将来你能对得起Grayson先生\NIn future I'd appreciate it if you tried to earn
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.20,0:09:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,对你的信任和慷慨\NMr. Grayson's trust, not to mention generosity,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.34,0:09:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,首先要做到的就是在商务洽谈的时候\Nand I'd start by sharing your undivided attention
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.54,0:09:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,一心一意\Nduring business meetings.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.94,0:09:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起  是我没有做好\NI'm sorry. There's no excuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.44,0:09:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我给你一份名单\NI provided a list of individuals
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.08,0:09:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Grayson先生非常希望你和他们\NMr. Grayson would very much like you
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.45,0:09:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,缔结友谊\Nto foster friendships with.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.51,0:09:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我确信名单上大部分人你都认识\NI'm sure you recognize most of the names on the list.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.45,0:09:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,还有  Harker\NAnd, Harker...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.42,0:09:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,再也不要在任何人面前  自作主张为我说话\NNever again presume to defend me to anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.16,0:09:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你愿意的话  我可以合成一种兴奋剂\NIf you wish, I'd be happy to mix a stimulant.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.76,0:09:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,现在可以告诉我  你的客户名了吗？\NNow may I inquire as to your client's name?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.47,0:09:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得不便透漏\NI'd rather not say.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.44,0:09:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  医生  又不是什么学术秘密\NPlease, doctor, indulge a humble academic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.68,0:10:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,那么  教授  我可以\NWell, professor, I suppose I can rely
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.35,0:10:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,信任你吧？\Non your discretion?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.02,0:10:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,是Jayne Wetherby女士\NShe is Lady Jayne Wetherby.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.56,0:10:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,啊\NAh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.89,0:10:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我懂了  懂了\NI see. I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.83,0:10:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的猎人在为她的先知寻找新药\NOur huntswoman is seeking a new drug for her seers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.00,0:10:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.27,0:10:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我非常确定\NI'm certain of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.87,0:10:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,把药给她\NGive it to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.98,0:10:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  如果你坚持的话  我会做一种\NWell, if you insist, I'll concoct a serum
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.15,0:10:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,药效不足的血清\Nof inadequate potency.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.28,0:10:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,好使我们的敌人另寻他法\NAnd force our enemy to seek a new solution elsewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.22,0:10:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们无法控制吗\Nbeyond our control.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.02,0:10:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,干的不错啊  Van Helsing\NWell done Van Helsing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.03,0:10:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,目光短浅  愚蠢荒唐\NShort-sighted and foolish.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.83,0:10:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,那你有更好的计划吗？\NI suppose you have a better plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.80,0:11:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,如果Grayson的地磁计划成功实施\NIf Grayson brings off his geomagnetic scheme,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.10,0:11:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,那恶龙会的石油股份\Nthe Order's oil and petroleum holdings
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.64,0:11:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,将会变得一文不值\Nwon't be worth the paper they're written on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.97,0:11:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我很清楚他对我们\NI am well aware of the threat he poses
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.47,0:11:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,所有人的威胁\Nto all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.61,0:11:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,那你发什么疯\NSo what on earth possessed you
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.88,0:11:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,把你冷剂公司的股份卖给他？\Nto sell him your shares in British Imperial Coolant?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.21,0:11:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我有别的选择\NHad I a choice in the matter,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.65,0:11:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我永远也不会同意他的条件\NI never would have agreed to his terms.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.99,0:11:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,他威胁你了\NHe threatened you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.35,0:11:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,对于违背誓言的兄弟\NThere is no protection, none,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.52,0:11:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,是不会提供一丁点保护的\Nfor any brother who violates the principal oath.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.63,0:11:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你想为自己辩护什么的话\NIf you have anything to say to me in your defense,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.89,0:11:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我建议你现在就说  否则就站在兄弟们面前\NI suggest you do so now or stand before your brothers
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.53,0:11:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,接受应有的惩罚\Nand suffer the punishment proscribed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.41,0:13:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,杀了我\NKill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.15,0:14:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,求你 杀了我吧\NPlease. Kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.55,0:14:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,嘘\NShh.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.11,0:15:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Grayson\NGrayson.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.52,0:15:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,这边请\NThis way, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.93,0:15:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,到了  女士\NHere we are. Madam.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.40,0:15:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Daniel  那是Alexander Grayson的人吗？\NDaniel, is that Alexander Grayson's man?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.51,0:15:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Jonathan Harker\NJonathan Harker.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.84,0:15:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  父亲  是他\NYes, father, that's him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.91,0:15:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Winston\NWinston.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.98,0:15:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,送瓶波尔多葡萄酒给那位年轻人\NWill you send a bottle of Bordeaux over to that young man
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.88,0:15:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,独自用餐的那位  Harker先生\Ndining on his own, Mr. Harker,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.98,0:15:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,以表心意\Nwith our compliments?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.85,0:15:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,有问题吗？\NIs there a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.82,0:15:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题  先生  只是Harker先生派我们\NNo, sir. It's just Mr. Harker directed us
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.99,0:15:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,把这个送给您  一点儿心意\Nto send this over with his compliments.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.93,0:16:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,1890年的拉图\NHmm, Latour 1890.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.63,0:16:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我们应该好好转转\NWe shall make a full circuit,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.94,0:16:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,从萨沃伊开始\Nstarting at the Savoy
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.10,0:16:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,然后晚点到达官员俱乐部舞会\Nand arriving fashionably late at the officers' club ball,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.47,0:16:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,那儿的男人肯定仪表堂堂  即使有点过于彬彬有礼\Nwhere the men shall be delicious, if a little too well-behaved.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.04,0:16:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy...  你来的时候\NLucy... When you went to the house,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.81,0:16:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你确定没看见Jonathan吗？\Nare you sure you didn't see Jonathan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.18,0:16:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,没有  Mina\NNo, Mina.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.39,0:16:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,一张便条  一张卡片都没见  什么也没有\NNot a note, not a card, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.99,0:16:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,显然他已经找到了适合他的蠢娘们\NNo doubt he's already found some silly little cow
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.23,0:16:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,当他所谓的“得体的英国妻子”\Nwho fits his description of a proper English wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.30,0:16:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我们该怎么对那些可心的官员们呢？\NWhat do we do with these delicious officers?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.60,0:16:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,女士们\NLadies.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.00,0:16:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(422,180)\c&H03FBF9&\fs24}詹姆斯旅馆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.04,0:17:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你要去哪儿？\NWhere are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.93,0:17:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道的  我得走了\NYou know I have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.46,0:17:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,像个夜贼一样偷偷溜走吗？\NTo steal away like a thief in the night?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.66,0:17:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,木已成舟\NThe die is cast.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.30,0:17:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,那我们逃吧\NThen we'll run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.86,0:17:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,逃得远远的  逃离恶龙社\NWe'll run as far and as fast as we can
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.43,0:17:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,逃到没有它束缚和法规的地方去\Nto a safe haven beyond the reach of the Order.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.80,0:17:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,没有这样的地方  Daniel\NThere's no such place, Daniel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.27,0:17:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道的\NAnd you know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.97,0:17:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,-那我们就坦承一切  -你疯了吗？\N- Then we'll simply come clean. - Are you mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.48,0:17:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我的名声怎么办？\NWhat of my reputation?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.94,0:17:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我可不愿为了苟活于世\NI will not shirk death
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.28,0:17:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,而让我的家族蒙羞\Nonly to see my family's legacy compromised.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.98,0:17:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,在我向那个美国人屈从的时候\NI signed my death warrant
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.35,0:17:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我已将生死置之度外\Nthe moment that I capitulated to that American.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.89,0:17:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我早就清楚会发生什么\NI knew this when I did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.39,0:17:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,再一次  我还会这样做的\NAnd I would do it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.03,0:17:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,停！\NStop!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.80,0:17:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,终于等来了\NFinally.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.20,0:17:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我们已经等了一整晚了\NWe've been waiting here all night.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.01,0:17:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,先生  太阳出来了\NSir, the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.37,0:18:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,再等会儿\NJust a moment more.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.45,0:18:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,什么东西\NWhat is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.21,0:18:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,先生\NSir.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.28,0:18:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我想看见\NI want to see her face
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.85,0:18:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,她读卡片时的表情\Nwhen she reads the card.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.89,0:18:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,是Jonathan写给你的吗？\NAre they from Jonathan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.62,0:18:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,-不是  -让我看看\N- No. - Oh, let me see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.69,0:18:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,很抱歉  先生\NI'm sorry, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.12,0:18:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,该死！\NDamn!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.66,0:18:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,“面对梦想  人人都可能会踟躇\N"When it comes to dreams, one might falter,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.79,0:18:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,但只要不放弃就不算失败\N"But the only way to fail is to abandon them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.96,0:18:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,恭贺”\NCongratulations."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.63,0:18:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,没署名\NIt's unsigned.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.63,0:18:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得会是谁送的\NWho do you think might have sent them?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.74,0:18:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\NI haven't the slightest.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.87,0:18:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.87,0:19:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你的免疫阳光研究有进展没？\NHave you made any progress with the solar vaccine?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.00,0:19:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,因为正在为Jayne女士研究血清  所以没有\NNot while devising the serum for Lady Jayne, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.57,0:19:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我还得在黑暗中躲藏多久？\NHow long must I spend skulking in the shadows?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.77,0:19:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我想像常人一样在阳光下行走\NI want to walk in the sun like any other man.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.07,0:19:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你永远不可能和常人一样\NYou will never be like any other man.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.94,0:19:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你给我记好了\NYou would do well to remember that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.08,0:19:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我把见光时间延长到了\NI've increased the duration of the vaccine
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.51,0:19:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,三分钟十二秒\Nto three minutes and 12 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.02,0:19:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,阿\NAh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.02,0:19:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,- 三分钟  - 零十二秒\N- Three minutes. - And 12 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.02,0:19:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你只给我留了在灰飞烟灭前\NYou leave me just enough time to have a cup of tea
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.82,0:19:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,喝杯茶的时间啊\Nbefore I burst into flames.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.28,0:20:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Stephen James Laurent兄弟\NBrother Stephen James Laurent,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.08,0:20:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你有把个人利益置于\Ndid you place your own interests before those
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.85,0:20:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,令人敬畏的秩序之上吗？\Nof this most august order?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.98,0:20:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,有\NI did.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.82,0:20:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,惩罚已在这里尽数列出\NThe punishment is proscribed within these pages.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.19,0:20:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,如之所书\NSo it is written...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.46,0:20:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,履之如规\NAnd so it shall be done.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.06,0:21:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,这些规矩是\NThe sentence has been handed down
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.06,0:21:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,代代相传\Nfrom generation to generation.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.20,0:21:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你甘愿接受刀刑吗？\NWill you accept the blade?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.34,0:21:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我愿意\NI will.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.90,0:22:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&H05F6DD&\fs22\pos(352,58)}我想我懂自己的感觉 \NI think I know how I feel.   
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.27,0:22:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(356,66)\c&H03FBF9&\fs22} 我只为你付出 \N I only pay it for you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.27,0:22:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(356,66)\c&H03FBF9&\fs22} 你该将我捧在手心\N You should be picking me up
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.88,0:22:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(356,66)\c&H03FBF9&\fs22} 你却将我抛在地上 \NInstead you're dragging me down 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.30,0:22:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,, {\pos(356,66)\c&H03FBF9&\fs22} 你在我头顶飞翔 \NYou flying over my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.30,0:22:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(356,66)\c&H03FBF9&\fs22} 降落在了镇子的每个角落\NYou're landing all over town.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.94,0:23:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,想什么呢？\NWhat are you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.15,0:23:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你…  你该再喝点苦艾酒\NAh, you... You need more absinthe.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.55,0:23:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,或许吧  但是通过研究实验\NPerhaps, but by way of careful study and experiment,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.45,0:23:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经知道我的酒量了\NI may have discovered my limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.75,0:23:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,才貌兼备啊\NBeautiful and witty.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.02,0:23:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道是该为你写首诗\NHmm, I'm not sure whether to write a poem
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.96,0:23:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,还是画幅画像呢\Nor paint your portrait.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.69,0:23:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我在想  你用纸张和花言巧语奉承过\NI wonder, how many women have you flattered with paper
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.86,0:24:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,多少女人呢？\Nand canvass?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.73,0:24:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你是最后一个  我保证\NYou're the last one. I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.34,0:24:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我是通过一个有限孔径\NMy way of contact with reality
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.37,0:24:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,来和现实接触的\Nis through a limited aperture.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.54,0:24:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我们之间的际遇会在那个小孔里…\NOur transfluence takes place through one small...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.92,0:24:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,发生\Nopening.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.52,0:24:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,很好笑吗？\NI amuse you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.72,0:24:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,女人们有为之倾倒的吗？\NDo women really fall for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.26,0:24:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,“际遇”\N"Transfluence."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.69,0:24:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你如此出众\NHow superior you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.39,0:24:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,像你这样的女人\NA woman of your means
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.60,0:24:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,来到低下的地方猎奇\Nslumming the lower depths.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.63,0:24:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,就像观察动物园的人一样观察着我们\NObserving us like we're animals at the zoo.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.70,0:24:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,啊\NAh.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.04,0:24:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,可这里没有栅栏\NYou see there are no bars here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.28,0:24:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我们也没有被关在笼子里\NAnd we are not caged.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.15,0:25:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,好了  我很好\NAll right. I'm fine. Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.16,0:25:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,滚！\NMove!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.24,0:25:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Grayson先生\NMr. Grayson.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.83,0:25:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你救我\NThank you for my rescue.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.43,0:25:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,不算什么\NIt was nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.93,0:25:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,但你来这做什么？\NBut what brought you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.14,0:25:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,这地方的派对众所周知\NThis place is notorious for its parties.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.81,0:25:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢那的音乐\NI like the music.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.94,0:25:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯\NHmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.11,0:25:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你有心事\NYou're troubled.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.31,0:25:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,- 没有  - 告诉我\N- No. - Tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.59,0:25:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托\NPlease.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.85,0:25:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,是和Jonathan的事\NIt's Jonathan.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.75,0:25:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Harker吗？\NHarker?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.92,0:25:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我不相信他会做任何伤害你的事\NI can't believe he'd do anything to hurt you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.16,0:26:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,但他做了\NBut he did.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.63,0:26:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,他对我说很不好的话  我就离开了\NHe said the most horrible things, and I walked away,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.50,0:26:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,那以后我们再也没见过面\Nand we haven't seen each other since.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.40,0:26:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道该怎么办\NI don't know how to fix it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.67,0:26:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(380,48)}（波西米亚夜生活：代表放纵）
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.77,0:26:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,波西米亚式的夜生活勉强算是快乐的替代品\NYou know, bohemian nightlife is a poor substitute for happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.95,0:26:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,有时我们命中注定的人和地方\NSometimes the people and places we are meant for
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.09,0:26:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,会使我们惊讶难耐\Ntake us by surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.72,0:26:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,这上演着戏剧呢\NWell, there's a tableau vivant.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.32,0:26:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,犹如沼泽里的Heathcliff和Cathy\NHeathcliff and Cathy on the moors.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.32,0:26:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(370,48)}（出自《呼啸山庄》）
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.53,0:26:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,天色已晚\NIt's getting late.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.23,0:26:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,-我可以送你们俩回家吗  -不用  谢谢\N- May I see you ladies home? - No. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.10,0:26:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的马车在外面等着呢\NOur carriage is waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.04,0:26:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安  Murray小姐  Westenra小姐\NMiss Murray, Miss Westenra.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.04,0:26:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢  Grayson先生\NThank you... Mr. Grayson.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.32,0:27:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,昨天我和你名单上列出的一些人共进午餐\NI had lunch with several of the men on your list yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.09,0:27:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Davenport先生和他的儿子\NDavenport and son,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.03,0:27:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Rothcroft大人  Shaw上将\NLord Rothcroft, General Shaw.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.93,0:27:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了  还有谁？\NI see. Anyone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.57,0:27:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Browning先生\NA Mr. Browning.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.07,0:27:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,-Browning？  -没错  他也参加了你的派对\N- Browning? - Yes, he was at your party.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.84,0:27:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你确定吗？\NAre you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.54,0:27:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,非常确定\NYes, quite.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.81,0:27:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,一个我们共同的朋友\NNow a mutual friend has told me
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.88,0:27:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,秘密地告诉我\Nin complete discretion of course
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.08,0:27:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,最近你和一位年轻女士闹矛盾了\Nthat you have recently broken from a young lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.89,0:27:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我忘了她的名字了\NHer name escapes me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.19,0:27:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Mina Murray.\NMina Murray.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.52,0:27:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,多迷人的姑娘\NCharming gal.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.66,0:27:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你不介意的话  我不想讨论这件事\NI'd rather not discuss it, if you don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.73,0:27:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,可我介意\NBut I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.36,0:27:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是防止你把我的书房\NIf only to prevent you from turning my study
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.93,0:27:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,变成殡仪馆\Ninto a funeral parlor.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.60,0:27:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起\NI'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.65,0:28:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我认识Murray小姐\NI've known Miss Murray...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.18,0:28:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Mina…很久了\NMina...for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.49,0:28:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,她一直很倔强\NShe's always been very stubborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.49,0:28:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,就算我打算娶她为妻  共度余生\NShe insists on continuing her studies despite the fact
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.29,0:28:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,她还是坚持要不顾世俗\Nthat I now have the means and every intention
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.50,0:28:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,继续她的学业\Nof supporting her as my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.07,0:28:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白了\NI understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.07,0:28:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,-你明白了？  - 嗯哼\N- You do? - Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.17,0:28:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白了你就是个傻瓜\NI understand that you are a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.31,0:28:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,一个想挑战世俗\NHow can a man who wishes to defy social convention
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.48,0:28:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,提升自己的男人\Nand rise above his station
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.88,0:28:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么会用世俗禁锢自己的爱人呢？\Ndeny the same thing in the woman he loves?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.89,0:28:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你是说我是个伪君子\NYou're calling me a hypocrite.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.15,0:28:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不  Harker\NNo, Harker.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.42,0:28:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我说你是个傻瓜\NI'm calling you a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.69,0:28:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,但你是个恋爱中的男人\NBut you are a man in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.86,0:29:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,恋爱中的男人都这样\NAnd they are very often the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.00,0:29:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,工作结束了  回家吧\NFinish up. Go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.95,0:29:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,恩\NMm.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.59,0:29:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你醒了\NYou're up.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.90,0:29:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,想事儿呢\NThinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.56,0:29:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  “思考啊”\NOh. "Thinking."
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.70,0:29:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我就是想想  你知道的  偶尔想想\NI do think, you know, every so often.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.87,0:29:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,那你想什么呢？\NAnd what are you thinking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.97,0:29:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你\NYou.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.34,0:29:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你鼓励我…\NYou inspire me to...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.41,0:29:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不知道怎么说  让我更自立了\NI don't know, greater independence, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.81,0:29:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,几点了？\NWhat time is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.98,0:29:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,两点\N2:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.98,0:30:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我们把半天时间赠予了黑夜啊\NWe gave half the day to the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.09,0:30:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,-两点？  - Mina  怎么了？\N-2:00? - Mina, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.62,0:30:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我错过了Van Helsing教授的课\NI missed Professor Van Helsing's class.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.43,0:30:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,薄荷能舒缓胃不适\NPeppermint to soothe the stomach,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.70,0:30:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,柳树皮会减轻头痛\Nwillow bark to ease the pounding in your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.47,0:30:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,苦口  却是良药\NIt tastes awful, but it will work wonders.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.97,0:30:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢  教授\NThank you, professor.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.01,0:30:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Murray小姐\NMiss Murray,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.01,0:30:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我是在你身上浪费时间吗？\Nam I wasting my time with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.28,0:30:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,有梦想就要有奋斗\NThere are dreams we must fight for.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.59,0:30:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你想冲出\NIf you want to advance beyond the boundaries
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.62,0:30:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,社会于你的禁锢\Nsociety has made for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.43,0:30:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你就要奋斗\Nyou must fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.49,0:30:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,您没有浪费您的时间\NYou're not wasting your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.86,0:30:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,再给我一次机会  我会证明给您\NGive me a second chance, and I will prove it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.47,0:31:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,明天早上5点整到这里\NReturn here tomorrow morning at 5:00 a.M. Sharp.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.31,0:31:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你这个学期要当我的助手\NYou will report to me as my assistant for the term.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.83,0:31:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,给Jayne夫人那先知的血清已经准备好了\NThe serum for Lady Jayne's seers is ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.24,0:31:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要寻本溯源\NWe'll track their power to its source,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.51,0:31:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,一场灾难将会降临这座城市\Nand there will be a plague upon this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.42,0:31:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,拿着这个直接到纸上的这个地址\NTake this directly to the address as written.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.72,0:31:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,别磨蹭\NDon't dawdle.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.76,0:31:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,如果一个小时内你带着签字的交货收据回来\NIf you return within an hour with a signed receipt of delivery,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.26,0:31:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,就再给你一先令作为奖励\Na second shilling will be your reward.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.89,0:31:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,- 去吧 - 好的 先生\N- Go on. - Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.83,0:32:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,好的  先生\NYes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.15,0:32:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,兴奋剂起效了吗 妹妹？\NIs the stimulant working, sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.09,0:32:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你能看到那个吸血鬼么？\NCan you see the vampire?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.56,0:32:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我能看到  兴奋剂有效果了\NI can see. It's working.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.53,0:33:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,那个吸血鬼  他和她在一起\NThe vampire. He's with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.56,0:33:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,救救我\NHelp me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.24,0:33:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我们被人下毒了\NWe've been poisoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.52,0:34:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我看到我的血清起效了\NI see my serum has taken hold.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.75,0:34:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,目前来看  你们都动不了了\NBy now you will both be paralyzed.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.49,0:34:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你们知道\NDo you have any idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.77,0:34:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,听到自己的妻儿的尖叫\Nwhat it's like to hear the screams
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.63,0:34:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,会是什么样的心情吗？\Nof your wife and children?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.88,0:34:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我的孩子要是活到现在也有20岁了\NMy children would be in their 20s now.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.45,0:34:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,就是因为惩罚我的不屈服\NThe Order burned them alive for no other reason
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.25,0:34:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,恶龙会就活活的烧死了他们\Nthan to punish me for my disobedience.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.72,0:34:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我失去了一切\NI lost everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.40,0:34:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你们在找的那个怪物\NThe monster you seek,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.73,0:35:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能让你们找到他\NI cannot let you find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.03,0:35:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,直到我们一劳永逸地摧毁了恶龙会\NNot as long as he is of use to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.47,0:35:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,他对我都会很有用\NUntil we've destroyed the Order once and for all.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.64,0:35:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我担心你们死后\NI'm afraid traces of the drug
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.24,0:35:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,毒药会残留在你们的脑组织里\Nwill stay in your brain tissue post-mortem.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.61,0:35:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,因为在英国  我是唯一的\NSince I'm the only man in Britain
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.32,0:35:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,拥有专门技术生产和管理\Nwho possesses the expertise to process and administer
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.92,0:35:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,这非致命药剂的人\Na non-lethal dose,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.06,0:35:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我会被怀疑的\NI would fall under suspicion.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.36,0:35:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我必须毁掉这个证据\NThis evidence I must destroy.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.26,0:35:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,很不幸  但有时科学就要有所牺牲\NIt is unfortunate, but sometimes science requires sacrifice.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.11,0:35:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,别担心  我动手很快\NDon't worry. I will be quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.58,0:36:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,就来了\NComing.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.92,0:36:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起\NI'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.16,0:36:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,为所有的事情\NFor everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.59,0:36:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,都是我的错  与你无关\NIt's my fault, not yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.16,0:36:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我太固执了  太沉迷于\NI've been stubborn and so obsessed
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.63,0:36:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,追求自己的梦想  从没花时间\Nwith chasing my own dreams I never even took the time
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.87,0:36:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,了解你的梦想  现在我了解了\Nto understand yours, and I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.30,0:36:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我意识到  你不需要我的保护\NBut I now realize you don't require my protection.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.41,0:36:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你不需要遵照世俗\NAnd you are in no need of keeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.44,0:36:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,那么  如果…如果可以\NSo, if... if you could,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.38,0:36:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,让我接着爱你\Njust let me love you instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.19,0:36:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安  Murray小姐\NGood evening, Miss Murray.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.90,0:37:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Jonathan!\NJonathan!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.14,0:37:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你忘了最重要的事\NYou've forgotten the most important thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.05,0:37:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,是什么？\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.95,0:37:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,娶我\NMarry me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.69,0:37:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,做我的丈夫  我做你的妻子\NBe my husband, and I will be your wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.20,0:37:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我曾经很多次的想向你求婚\NI wanted to ask you so many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.90,0:37:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我甚至买了一枚戒指\NI even bought a ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.37,0:37:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,等下\NWait.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.91,0:37:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以么？\NMay I?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.25,0:38:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我今天碰到的最奇怪的事\NThe oddest thing happened to me today.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.18,0:38:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗  先生  就一件？\NReally, sir? Just one?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.15,0:38:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我表演了一番  让他人得到的欢乐\NI performed an act which brought great joy
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.02,0:38:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,比我的快乐还要多\Nto someone other than myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.06,0:38:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,谁？\NWhom?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.49,0:38:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Harker  还有 Mina Murray.\NHarker, Mina Murray.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.43,0:38:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,那您到底做了什么？\NWhat exactly did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.37,0:38:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我引导他们回到彼此身边\NI guided the one back to the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.03,0:38:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,现在看来  他们会结婚\NBy the looks of it, they'll be wed.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.37,0:38:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,那是件好事\NA good deed then.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.24,0:38:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.14,0:38:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我应该惊骇\NI should be horrified.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.11,0:39:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,但说实话  我并不反感这感觉\NBut in truth I can't say I dislike this feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.35,0:39:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,- 但是…  - 但是\N- And yet... - And yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.42,0:39:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,让你的雇员和Murray小姐在一起\NKeeping your employee and Miss Murray together
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.59,0:39:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,就是把她留在您的生活轨道内\Nkeeps her in your orbit.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.56,0:39:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,就像重力  恰到好处  不远不近\NLike gravity. Close but not too close.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.46,0:39:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,可让她离去也许更明智\NWhen it might be wiser to let her go.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.13,0:39:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,有时候过于聪明对你没好处\NSometimes you're too smart for your own good.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.74,0:39:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,就像一个磨盘挂在我脖子上  是个负担\NIt's like a millstone around my neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.98,0:39:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,那天早上\NOn that first morning
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.88,0:39:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,他们造就了我\Nwhen they made me what I am,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.01,0:39:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,阳光灼烧我的皮肤\Nthe sunlight burned my skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.35,0:39:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不知何情  不晓何故\NI don't know how or why,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.26,0:39:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,但我就知道我不一样了\Nbut I knew I would never be the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.73,0:39:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你做了什么？\NWhat did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.46,0:39:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,扯掉了混蛋牧师的喉咙\NRipped out the throat of the bastard priest.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.67,0:40:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,所以  总的来说  不是个糟糕的早晨\NSo not a bad morning, all things considered.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.11,0:40:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我经历过更糟糕的\NI've had worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.12,0:40:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么会这样？\NHow can this be?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.82,0:40:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\NI don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.79,0:40:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,从未有过\NIt's unprecedented.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.76,0:40:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,反向追踪…之前从未发生过\NTo track the trackers... It has never been done before.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.13,0:40:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这是场灾难  - 哦  还有更糟的\N- It's a disaster. - Oh, it's worse than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.93,0:40:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我在找的那个吸血鬼干的\NThis is the work of the vampire that I seek.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.10,0:40:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,由于先知死了\NNow that the seers are dead,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.24,0:40:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,他能够更容易的吸引来他的族类\Nhe will much more easily attract others of his kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.11,0:40:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶\NAn abomination.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.24,0:40:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,很快伦敦就会挤满了这些毒物\NSoon London will be crawling with the vermin.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.23,0:41:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Stephen.\NStephen.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.60,0:41:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Daniel!\NDaniel!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.04,0:41:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,哦  我的孩子！\NOh, my boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.40,0:42:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Grayson.\NGrayson.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.10,0:42:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Grayson!\NGrayson!
